title: Professor Kliq Discography
description:
Professor Kliq discography containing the following albums:


Our Universe (2005)

Guns Blazin (2008)

The Scientific Method, Volume II: Experiments in Sound & Perspective (2008)

Community Service (2009)

Community Service II (2009)

Movements EP (2010)

Athene's Theory of Everything: The Original Soundtrack (2011)

Feel free to leave a comment about any releases or any other details I may have missed.
